      <bpmn2:documentation id="_SXXYU0DuEfGrK4FBZUBLpg"><![CDATA[Finds place bound to a given addressCrossId. Output resultList may be null or empty - downstream gateway will branch to Create place in that case.]]></bpmn2:documentation>
